Author: anathebasic
Text: yeah exactly! I feel like this is some sort of cosmic joke and I'll end up stepping on a scale at a friend's house that'll tell me I'm 130 or something. And thank you for the advice :) I should be glad that my body has been functioning well when I've been unknowingly restricting, hopefully I can see the results by the time exams are over!

Author: VengefulBodied
Text: Wow! I know you're kinda freaking out but hey why question unexpected good things right? I get weirded out when somehow I've lost weight after a binge, like is it a trap or is the universe fucking with me?  But seriously congratulations! I think it's just body dysmorphia, if you can maintain that for a couple weeks maybe you'll be able to see the change yourself.
